### 1. Register admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "admin",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 2. Register user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "user",
  "password": "user123",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 3. Login user. Скопируй token из ответа.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "user",
  "password": "user123"
}

### 4. Generate OTP to file. Вставь USER_TOKEN.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/otp/generate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

{
  "operationId": "operation-1",
  "email": "",
  "phone": "",
  "telegramDestination": "",
  "sendEmail": false,
  "sendSms": false,
  "sendTelegram": false,
  "saveToFile": true
}

### 5. Validate OTP. Код возьми из otp-codes.txt.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/user/otp/validate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer USER_TOKEN

{
  "operationId": "operation-1",
  "code": "123456"
}

### 6. Login admin. Скопируй token из ответа.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "login": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 7. Get users. Вставь ADMIN_TOKEN.
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

### 8. Get OTP config
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/otp-config
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

### 9. Update OTP config
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/admin/otp-config
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer ADMIN_TOKEN

{
  "codeLength": 6,
  "ttlSeconds": 300
}
